### 查询所有用户 / Get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/users

### 查询单个用户 / Get user by username
GET http://localhost:8080/users/tom

### 注册用户 / Register user
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "spring01",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 用户登录 / Login
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "tom",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 修改密码 / Change password
PUT http://localhost:8080/users/spring01/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "abcdef"
}

### 使用新密码登录 / Login with new password
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "spring01",
  "password": "abcdef"
}

### 删除用户 / Delete user
DELETE http://localhost:8080/users/spring01

